1. How many types of conditions are available in conditional formatting on Excel?
  There are 2 types of conditions in conditional formatting
    Highlight cell rules, Top/Bottom rules are major rules in conditional formatting.

2. How to insert border in Excel with Format Cells dialog?
  Select the cells then click borders in home page. Then insert border with given options

3. How to Format Numbers as Currency in Excel?
   Select the column then right click then in the dialog box click $ symbol then give the currency.

4. What are the steps to format numbers in Excel with the Percent style?
  Select the column then right click then in the dialog box click % symbol then number changes to percentage.

5. What is a shortcut to merge two or more cells in excel?
  Select the cells then click Alt + H + M + M

6. How do you use text commands in Excel?
  Select the cells and =Text(Value, format_text)
